<template>
    <v-btn
        :width="width"
        color="primary"
        class="py-6"
        depressed
        v-on="$listeners"
        >{{ text }}</v-btn
    >
</template>

<script>
export default {
    name: 'CustomButton',
    props: {
        text: String,
        width: String,
    },
};
</script>

<style lang="scss" scoped>
.button {
    padding: 16px;
    background-color: var(--main);
    color: white;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 500;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 5px;
    width: 100%;

    &:hover {
        background-color: var(--main-hover);
        cursor: pointer;
    }
}
</style>
